WEBVTT

00:00:02.560 --> 00:00:06.384
TAPE NUMBER FOUR, INTERVIEW WITH MISTER KALMAN SHLOMOVICH.

00:00:07.048 --> 00:00:08.425
YOU'RE,

00:00:14.490 --> 00:00:16.121
ver hot dos gezen?

00:00:18.996 --> 00:00:23.157
keyner hot nisht gevezn dort, tsvey ofitsirn

00:00:23.265 --> 00:00:27.275
hobn mikh geshlogn, eyner un tsu bislekh ongehoybn

00:00:27.366 --> 00:00:29.840
eyner, ven deys iz oyfgehert

00:00:29.998 --> 00:00:31.494
hot er der tsveyter,

00:00:31.887 --> 00:00:36.252
ikh gedenk ikh hob getseylt a por biz finef zeks, vayter hob ikh nisht getseylt.

00:00:36.917 --> 00:00:38.801
un m'hot mikh aroysgevorfn

00:00:39.904 --> 00:00:41.096
hob ikh nisht gekent

00:00:41.187 --> 00:00:45.332
mer zayn oyf zitsn, nisht lign, nisht gornisht.

00:00:46.992 --> 00:00:49.705
oyf der nakht ven m'iz gegangen fun der arbet avek,

00:00:49.705 --> 00:00:52.723
gevezn mayne khaveyrim vos m'hot gearbet tsuzamen,

00:00:52.932 --> 00:00:54.731
ikh veys nisht ver pinktlekh,

00:00:55.547 --> 00:00:58.140
hobn genumen oyf azelkhe heltser,

00:00:58.618 --> 00:01:01.801
deys mikh aroyfgeleygt un m'hot mikh arayngebrengt in

00:01:02.044 --> 00:01:03.590
in lager arayn.

00:01:05.284 --> 00:01:09.513
ikh kum on in lager, hot men mikh aropgeleygt, zenen avekgegangen yeder khapn vos m'get oyf der nakht

00:01:09.705 --> 00:01:10.829
dos esn,

00:01:11.933 --> 00:01:15.066
ikh bin gelegn gelegn, ikh hob nisht gehat keyn breyre,

00:01:15.561 --> 00:01:18.002
ikh hob mikh un avekgegangen in

00:01:18.548 --> 00:01:20.837
oyfn bet, un ikh hob mikh aropgeleygt oyfn boykh,

00:01:21.754 --> 00:01:22.845
ikh bin gelegn.

00:01:25.281 --> 00:01:26.490
in der fri,

00:01:26.597 --> 00:01:28.177
iz azoy, ober

00:01:28.268 --> 00:01:32.379
du geyst oyf der arbet, ober du geyst in revir meldn zikh az du bist krank,

00:01:35.322 --> 00:01:42.926
SO bin ikh gekumen in der fri, bin ikh gegangen, vayl du host gemuzt aroysgeyn fun dem funem fun der barakn,

00:01:43.978 --> 00:01:45.831
bin ikh gekumen tsun a dokter,

00:01:45.831 --> 00:01:47.769
velkher iz geven, zog ikh im,

00:01:48.366 --> 00:01:52.815
azoy un azoy, ikh ken nisht oyf der arbet, ikh bin azoy tseshlogn deys,

00:01:53.040 --> 00:01:54.336
gib mir frey,

00:01:54.336 --> 00:01:57.202
a a dray fir tog, az ikh zol...

00:01:58.069 --> 00:02:01.117
zogt er, ikh ken dir dos nisht tun, ikh ken nisht gebn di...

00:02:00.043 --> 00:02:03.294
di di dokter iz geven a daytsh tsi a yid?

00:02:02.153 --> 00:02:03.244
a yid.

00:02:03.756 --> 00:02:05.775
ikh ken nisht gebn, zogt er, vayl

00:02:06.051 --> 00:02:09.381
azoy fil mentshn, azoy zey felt oys mentshn oyf der arbet,

00:02:09.381 --> 00:02:12.002
ikh ken nisht gebn keyn

00:02:12.210 --> 00:02:13.858
fray dir keyn deys.

00:02:14.843 --> 00:02:18.735
eyn zakh kenstu tun, kenst ara- arayngeyn in revir arayn.

00:02:19.416 --> 00:02:21.080
a revir hot dos geheysn.

00:02:22.572 --> 00:02:27.814
hot mir zeyer deys, vayl ikh hob gevust in der revir, keyner iz nokh nisht aroysgegangen fun dem revir.

00:02:28.647 --> 00:02:30.598
m'hot keyn meditsin nisht gegebn,

00:02:31.802 --> 00:02:34.631
bist gekumen in revir, hot men dikh oysgetun naket,

00:02:36.223 --> 00:02:37.685
aropgenumen ales,

00:02:38.333 --> 00:02:40.554
un m'hot dikh gegebn a kots eynemer.

00:02:40.662 --> 00:02:41.820
s'gevezn,

00:02:41.843 --> 00:02:42.866
a vos?

00:02:42.568 --> 00:02:46.309
aza a tsu tsudekn zikh, aza,

00:02:49.825 --> 00:02:51.456
un du host zikh gemuzt

00:02:51.867 --> 00:02:56.400
geyn ven m'hot gemakht tseylungen, in der fri un oyf der nakht apel,

00:02:56.878 --> 00:02:58.588
hot gemuzt geyn aroys,

00:02:58.588 --> 00:03:00.990
v- hot men, m'zol tseyln derfun.

00:03:05.350 --> 00:03:09.714
SO dos iz geven zeyer a shvere deys, naketerheyt, s'nokh gevezn

00:03:11.526 --> 00:03:14.084
s'gevezn peysekh tsayt,

00:03:15.508 --> 00:03:17.240
fleg'mir zikh tsunam shtupn

00:03:17.398 --> 00:03:19.096
azoy eyns in andern,

00:03:20.622 --> 00:03:22.736
flegn mir nemen der der Nevyum,

00:03:22.736 --> 00:03:25.357
iz gevezn a a royber dort der der...

00:03:25.397 --> 00:03:26.302
hot er,

00:03:26.882 --> 00:03:28.276
fleg er zogn,

00:03:28.806 --> 00:03:32.816
aroyfgekhapt dem der fun aza oyvn,

00:03:33.042 --> 00:03:35.584
er hot a vorf getun tsvishn di mentshn,

00:03:36.602 --> 00:03:38.536
geven a kha- a khaye.

00:03:39.673 --> 00:03:42.902
un fleg, vi vifl vifl hob ikh getrofn? vifl zenen toyte?

00:03:42.902 --> 00:03:46.958
mentshn zenen gevezn deys, vayl er hot gefaln iz sh- iz er meyle geven halb toyter,

00:03:48.381 --> 00:03:53.825
zogt er, s'nisht keyn feler, zogt er, vet ir geyn gikher, di ver s'iz deys vet geyn gikher in krematoryum, ir vet geyn dernokh dem.

00:03:53.950 --> 00:03:56.216
deys iz gevezn dort un fun dort hot men...

00:03:56.216 --> 00:03:57.858
undz ho'mir aleyn gezen,

00:03:58.017 --> 00:04:00.609
vi azoy m'hot geleygt di mentshn oyf di vagondlekh,

00:04:01.240 --> 00:04:04.136
ge- geleygt azoy vi f- hering,

00:04:05.138 --> 00:04:11.826
ikh hob tsugekukt vi azoy mentshn shlepn oyf di hent, er dreyt mitn moyl, farshteyst, deys, er iz shoyn gepakt in dem,

00:04:11.826 --> 00:04:14.852
gezen deys undzer letster...

00:04:16.528 --> 00:04:18.580
bin ikh gevezn tsuzamen

00:04:18.637 --> 00:04:22.344
mit mayne a kuzin, der iz shoyn nebekh geshtorbn nisht lang,

00:04:22.637 --> 00:04:23.930
Moyshe Volf,

00:04:24.966 --> 00:04:26.715
zogt er, her mir oys Kalmen,

00:04:28.223 --> 00:04:29.333
do iz do

00:04:29.333 --> 00:04:31.304
a plats eyner oyvn

00:04:32.172 --> 00:04:34.360
oyfn sh- oyfn betl fun oyvn,

00:04:34.720 --> 00:04:38.662
der velkher zenen in di betlekh tseylt men dort, broykh nisht aroysgeyn,

00:04:40.137 --> 00:04:41.694
un do ho'mir undz eynem

00:04:41.694 --> 00:04:43.927
vos er iz shoyn toyt a por tog,

00:04:44.743 --> 00:04:48.483
m'zetst im oyf, un m'nemt oyf im di shtikl broyt,

00:04:51.308 --> 00:04:55.639
SO do iz di khevre, ikh hob mit zey geshmuest, zey nemen dikh arayn,

00:04:56.202 --> 00:05:01.933
ober du muzt zey tsugebn dos broyt mitn zup vos du bakumst, darfstu dos gebn far zey.

00:05:03.610 --> 00:05:06.290
zog ikh, her, az ikh vel zey gebn dos broyt un di zup,

00:05:06.290 --> 00:05:08.548
vel ikh shoyn nisht darfn morgn keyn deys.

00:05:09.111 --> 00:05:12.711
veystu vos, ikh nem, ikh gib zey ober di zup, vos zey veln.

00:05:12.711 --> 00:05:14.541
koydem, zogt er, zog zey gornisht,

00:05:14.541 --> 00:05:15.804
koydem kum aroyf.

00:05:15.810 --> 00:05:18.554
m'hot nisht getort aleyn aroyfgeyn, dos iz nor vemen m'hot gelozt,

00:05:18.780 --> 00:05:25.422
iz gegangen, hot men dem toytn genumen, aropge- -numen funem betl, aroysgevor- untern betl,

00:05:26.965 --> 00:05:29.777
un ikh hob mir dort arayngezetst, dort ze'mir undz gevezn

00:05:31.032 --> 00:05:35.768
tsvey in eyn zayt, un tsvey in der andere zayt, di fus hot men gehaltn nor azoy deys,

00:05:38.102 --> 00:05:40.526
un khotshik ikh hob mir nisht gebroykht aropgeyn deye

00:05:41.022 --> 00:05:44.323
khevre hobn ge- farlangt ikh zol zey gebn vos ikh hob zey tsugezogt,

00:05:44.515 --> 00:05:45.774
zog ikh, herts oys,

00:05:46.506 --> 00:05:48.947
ikh geb aykh eyns, UNK hobn zikh

00:05:49.425 --> 00:05:51.410
ibergelozt, nor undz hobn genumen

00:05:51.923 --> 00:05:54.583
eyn tog der broyt, dos dem andern tog di zup.

00:05:56.631 --> 00:05:59.004
un azoy ho'mir gevart undzer shure

00:05:59.061 --> 00:06:00.860
in krematoryum arayn.

00:06:01.120 --> 00:06:04.219
vos du host geven in lager oder in revir?

00:06:04.039 --> 00:06:06.564
dos iz in revir gevezn, yo.

00:06:05.035 --> 00:06:06.061
in revir.

00:06:06.061 --> 00:06:10.243
un ver hot gefirt di komande az m'zol aykh,

00:06:10.317 --> 00:06:13.652
ver hot aykh gezogt az ir ken darf gebn zup oder,

00:06:13.742 --> 00:06:17.747
di mentshn vos zenen geze- vos zenen gehat dort ineveynik, deye hobn gezo-

00:06:17.747 --> 00:06:24.232
un zey hobn zikh gehaltn dem toytn, farshteyst, zey flegn zey oyf im nemen deys, un hobn zikh tseteylt mit dem di ale fir vos zenen gezesn dort.

00:06:23.867 --> 00:06:25.143
ale yidn?

00:06:24.880 --> 00:06:26.055
yidn, yo.

00:06:26.871 --> 00:06:28.226
hob ikh zey

00:06:28.226 --> 00:06:33.952
gegebn eyn mol di zup, eyn tog, un zey hobn zikh tseteylt, azoy bin ikh geblibn dort lebn mit zey deys.

00:06:34.566 --> 00:06:37.159
un dort bin ikh bafrayt gevorn, oyf dem

00:06:37.401 --> 00:06:38.644
oyf dem betl.

00:06:38.852 --> 00:06:42.018
oyfn andern betl iz gele- iz geven der

00:06:42.143 --> 00:06:43.622
dokter Fishbeyn.

00:06:44.016 --> 00:06:45.295
er iz gevezn

00:06:45.295 --> 00:06:46.676
an advokat,

00:06:47.121 --> 00:06:50.473
un der advokat iz gevezn, er hot gehat in OFFICE

00:06:50.968 --> 00:06:52.413
hot er gehat

00:06:53.584 --> 00:06:58.944
bakante vos hobn zikh gelernt in Prag tsuzamen mit im, un zey zenen gevezn in OFFICE,

00:06:59.440 --> 00:07:01.087
un zey hobn gezogt

00:07:01.448 --> 00:07:05.509
hobn im gegebn tsu visn ales, dort ho'mir shoyn gevust ales vos s'tut zikh.

00:07:06.392 --> 00:07:13.828
az m'geyt bafrayt vern, az di amerikaner ober di englender, s'geven gemisht, ver s'kumt arayn.

00:07:14.745 --> 00:07:16.241
eyn mol ruft er mikh,

00:07:16.382 --> 00:07:18.857
zogt er, her oys Kalmen,

00:07:19.791 --> 00:07:23.222
ikh hob bakumen a a deys az der nakht e'mir bafrayt vern.

00:07:23.222 --> 00:07:30.248
ober der lager firer vil ale araynfirn in tunel un vil zey oyfraysn.

00:07:31.080 --> 00:07:35.090
SO az m'vet kumen un m'vet shrayen s'apel, yeder muz aropgeyn

00:07:35.468 --> 00:07:37.082
ales yeder muz aropgeyn,

00:07:37.982 --> 00:07:39.359
zol keyner nisht geyn.

00:07:40.193 --> 00:07:45.536
un m'hot es azoy eyner funem andern fun di betlekh, azoy tsetrogn bald, in finef minut hot men gevust yeder.

00:07:46.892 --> 00:07:48.602
un s'azoy gevezn bay nakht,

00:07:48.602 --> 00:07:51.139
m'hot ongetsundn di lekters un m'hot onge- yeder

00:07:51.803 --> 00:07:54.632
aroys, m'geyt apel, m'geyt tseyln.

00:07:55.667 --> 00:07:57.011
keyner iz nisht gegangen.

00:07:57.658 --> 00:07:59.474
zey zenen zeyer broygez gevorn,

00:07:59.903 --> 00:08:02.023
ikh bin gevezn oyfn dritn betl,

00:08:03.042 --> 00:08:05.803
ikh hob, afile ven ikh vil ven ken ikh mimeyle nisht aropgeyn,

00:08:06.788 --> 00:08:10.523
ober zey hobn genumen un zey hobn ongehoybn mit di tushn, mit di

00:08:10.523 --> 00:08:12.995
biksn tsu klopn, nisht shisn,

00:08:12.995 --> 00:08:15.388
az tsu klopn m'zol geyn aroys.

00:08:15.698 --> 00:08:18.510
keyner hot nisht gevolt geyn, s'mir ales eyns, m'geyt im shisn.

00:08:19.275 --> 00:08:23.656
SO fun der ershter betl, fun UNK der tsveytn betl, vos zey hobn oysgeharget

00:08:23.697 --> 00:08:27.218
in der fri hot men getrofn bay zeks hundert mentshn, zenen geven toyt.

00:08:27.730 --> 00:08:29.124
fun der vos deys.

00:08:29.417 --> 00:08:30.477
nokh alemen,

00:08:30.477 --> 00:08:31.976
iz tunkl gevorn,

00:08:33.619 --> 00:08:34.912
un zenen avekgegangen.

00:08:36.201 --> 00:08:37.967
ven s'hot ongehoybn tsu

00:08:38.395 --> 00:08:39.671
tsu baginen,

00:08:42.225 --> 00:08:47.045
iz gevezn fun oyvn, un ikh veys nisht mit velkhn koyekh ikh hob mikh oyfgezetst,

00:08:47.170 --> 00:08:48.550
un vayzt mir

00:08:48.550 --> 00:08:54.234
kuk on di s'di ler, di vu m'hot gehit di lager, s'iz ler, s'iz keyner nishto.

00:08:55.388 --> 00:08:57.322
zey zenen avekgelofn bay nakht,

00:08:58.662 --> 00:09:01.544
un oyf dem aroyf zenen arayngekumen shoyn di

00:09:01.544 --> 00:09:04.883
amerikaner, tsi di englender, undz ho'mir nisht gevust keyn khilek,

00:09:07.656 --> 00:09:09.281
s'gekumen der

00:09:09.281 --> 00:09:13.168
