00:09:17.427 --> 00:09:20.813
zey zenen gekumen tsu loyfn mir un zey hobn gebrengt esn,

00:09:21.207 --> 00:09:24.486
zey hobn gebrengt a zak mit broyt far di gantse deys,

00:09:24.486 --> 00:09:25.909
ver hot gekent esn?

00:09:28.058 --> 00:09:32.506
ober s'gevezn, s'gekumen der NURSES,

00:09:33.930 --> 00:09:36.573
