hot men undz arum gebrengt,

00:12:53.308 --> 00:12:56.930
nisht mikh eyner aleyn, merer, hot men gebrengt tsurik in lager arayn.

00:12:58.793 --> 00:13:00.964
ikh bin ober geven nokh zeyer shvakh,

00:13:01.695 --> 00:13:03.123
in velkhn lager?

00:13:03.062 --> 00:13:06.155
in in oyf Ebnze tsurik in lager.

00:13:03.754 --> 00:13:06.228
in Eb- Ebnze, yo.

00:13:06.155 --> 00:13:09.654
dort iz shoyn geven a DIFFERENT deys, dort hob ikh gezen di ale

00:13:10.369 --> 00:13:16.320
yinglekh velkhe zenen gevezn, hobn getoygt a bisl, vos zenen geven in di kukhn gearbet, un vos zenen gevezn deys,

00:13:16.393 --> 00:13:21.216
zey zenen gegangen mit di gevern,

00:13:21.216 --> 00:13:23.863
un zey hobn gearbet mit der, vos zey hobn getun.

00:13:23.987 --> 00:13:26.006
zey hobn gelozt grobn griber

00:13:26.687 --> 00:13:32.688
far der s'geven a sakh mentshn vos zey hobn zey hobn oysgeharget, vos zenen geven, vos zey hot men nisht gehat baerdikt.

00:13:32.982 --> 00:13:36.013
hobn zey gegrobn di griber un m'hot zey baerdikt.

00:13:37.842 --> 00:13:39.996
SO ze'mir dort gevezn,

00:13:40.103 --> 00:13:43.185
dort hot men undz shoyn gegebn esn, s'geven fun alemen.

00:13:44.592 --> 00:13:46.206
ober m'hot gevolt heym.

00:13:48.608 --> 00:13:50.019
vu hot ir a heym?

00:13:50.818 --> 00:13:53.344
s'geven amerikaner deys,

00:13:54.092 --> 00:13:56.229
host epes eynem in Amerike?

00:13:56.252 --> 00:13:57.883
kenstu forn oyf Amerike.

00:13:58.581 --> 00:14:04.667
ikh hob, ikh veys ober nisht keyn adres, ikh hob nisht vemen, ikh hob nisht keyn telefon, ikh hob gornisht, ikh veys nisht.

00:14:06.023 --> 00:14:07.974
ikh hob gehat nokh demolts a feter

00:14:08.436 --> 00:14:11.180
un a mume hot gelebt in Klivland.

00:14:15.658 --> 00:14:17.660
ober ikh hob nisht gevust

00:14:17.886 --> 00:14:22.284
vu zey, vu vu zey gefinen zikh, dem a- di adres iz geblibn in der heym,

00:14:22.543 --> 00:14:25.017
undz ho'mir gehat mit im mitgenumen, ober

00:14:25.041 --> 00:14:29.152
s'gevezn in di papirn ober dos iz nokh ales ibergelozt in Oyshvits.

00:14:32.044 --> 00:14:33.897
azoy hot men undz gebrengt in a,

00:14:33.897 --> 00:14:35.733
ir zent a tshekhisher

00:14:35.790 --> 00:14:41.623
untergeber, dey, hot men undz gebrengt in a tshekhishn lager, oyf links, oykh in in dort s'gevezn

00:14:41.629 --> 00:14:45.217
hot men oysge- dort iz gevezn tshekhn, hot men undz ahin arayngebrengt.

00:14:46.371 --> 00:14:50.904
dort iz shoyn gevezn azoy, ze'mir gegan- arumgegangen un s'gevezn a kokh,

00:14:52.952 --> 00:14:54.870
un mir ze'mir arumgegangen

00:14:56.952 --> 00:14:58.195
biz vant

00:14:58.605 --> 00:15:02.598
s'nisht gekumen oytos un m'hot undz gefirt vayter.

00:15:03.212 --> 00:15:04.466
m'hot undz gebrengt

00:15:04.466 --> 00:15:05.619
oyf Prag.

00:15:06.790 --> 00:15:08.303
ver hot aykh gebrakht?

00:15:08.140 --> 00:15:09.146
di tshekhn.

00:15:08.882 --> 00:15:09.568
di tshekhn.

00:15:09.338 --> 00:15:11.469
tshekhn zenen gekumen mit

00:15:11.469 --> 00:15:15.845
mit oytobusn, m'hot gelodnt, un deys un zey hobn undz gebrengt oyf Prag.

00:15:17.657 --> 00:15:19.760
un ze'mir gekumen oyf Prag,

00:15:19.986 --> 00:15:21.836
zey hobn a kuk getun vi azoy

00:15:21.910 --> 00:15:23.861
ikh un mayn khaver,

00:15:24.475 --> 00:15:26.561
m'hot undz arayngeleygt in shpitol,

00:15:27.917 --> 00:15:30.816
ikh bin gevezn dray fir vokhn bin ikh gevezn in shpitol,

00:15:30.816 --> 00:15:32.164
a bisl tsugekumen,

00:15:34.060 --> 00:15:35.741
dort iz es gevezn

00:15:36.253 --> 00:15:38.086
gekumen bazukhn tshekhn,

00:15:39.713 --> 00:15:44.803
s'gekumen a froy eyne, un zi hot zikh tsu mir deys,

00:15:44.961 --> 00:15:48.279
ikh ze oys azoy vi ir zun velkher iz geharget gevorn

00:15:49.028 --> 00:15:51.047
un ikh darf zayn ir zun.

00:15:51.390 --> 00:15:52.897
un zi vil mikh nemen

00:15:52.897 --> 00:15:54.399
un vil mikh adoptirn,

00:15:54.399 --> 00:15:55.654
un zayn deys.

00:15:56.284 --> 00:15:58.120
koydem hot zi mikh genumen aheym,

00:15:58.120 --> 00:16:01.341
m'hot mikh opgevashn vi a deys un ongetun mikh sheyn,

00:16:01.920 --> 00:16:04.901
a tshekhishe yid oder?

00:16:02.832 --> 00:16:04.786
a tshekhishe, nisht keyn yid.

00:16:04.786 --> 00:16:05.714
nisht keyn yid.

00:16:05.714 --> 00:16:06.656
a tshekh.

00:16:06.915 --> 00:16:08.917
zi hot nisht geha- iz geven eyne aleyn.

00:16:10.864 --> 00:16:12.748
un zi hot mikh ongetun

00:16:13.345 --> 00:16:14.379
un zi zogt,

00:16:14.379 --> 00:16:16.269
kumst aroys funem shpitol,

00:16:16.269 --> 00:16:17.675
kenst voynen bay mir.

00:16:17.918 --> 00:16:19.329
un zayn mayn kind.

00:16:21.192 --> 00:16:22.570
un ikh zog ir,

00:16:22.727 --> 00:16:25.792
ikh veys vos a farmegn undz ho'mir ibergelozt in der heym,

00:16:26.592 --> 00:16:29.522
ikh ken nisht blaybn, ikh vil geyn aheym, un do veys ikh

00:16:29.882 --> 00:16:31.546
vegn dem kontrakt,

00:16:31.890 --> 00:16:35.883
yener vet zen az keyner iz nisht gekumen vet er tsunemen dos hoyz.

00:16:36.126 --> 00:16:37.318
der Sholye.

00:16:40.193 --> 00:16:43.106
un azoy iz gevezn. zog ikh far ir, her oys,

00:16:43.838 --> 00:16:45.657
ikh gey aheym,

00:16:45.657 --> 00:16:46.971
ikh gey zen.

00:16:47.702 --> 00:16:53.703
zogt zi mir, du darfst nisht geyn zen, du host nisht keyn mame, s'nishto keyner far dem, vayl ven s'iz do,

00:16:53.710 --> 00:16:55.071
vestu gevust.

00:16:57.220 --> 00:16:59.931
zog ikh, ales eyns, ikh muz geyn aheym.

00:17:00.055 --> 00:17:03.019
m'hot mir gegebn dort papirn,

00:17:03.042 --> 00:17:04.774
in Prag,

00:17:04.847 --> 00:17:06.039
UNK,

00:17:07.092 --> 00:17:09.246
un azoy bin ikh geforn

00:17:09.791 --> 00:17:11.320
biz Budapest.

00:17:12.880 --> 00:17:14.961
vayl oyf

00:17:14.961 --> 00:17:16.893
tsu undz hot men nisht gekent forn,

00:17:16.893 --> 00:17:21.210
vayl s'gevezn der tunel iz gevezn farklopt fun der shlakht oys,

00:17:21.704 --> 00:17:23.419
kumen oyf Budapest,

00:17:27.156 --> 00:17:28.466
oyfn veg

00:17:28.911 --> 00:17:30.486
ze'mir geshtanen in

00:17:30.486 --> 00:17:31.622
Preshburg.

00:17:32.455 --> 00:17:33.731
Bratislava.

00:17:35.374 --> 00:17:40.042
dort iz gevezn soldatn,

00:17:40.453 --> 00:17:42.084
rusishe soldatn,

00:17:42.765 --> 00:17:47.315
ikh hob gehat ontuekhts vos der hot mir gegebn zeyer sheyne k- deys,

00:17:47.592 --> 00:17:50.001
hob ikh ven ikh for in di tseger,

00:17:50.001 --> 00:17:53.474
leyg ikh ir arayn, hot zi mir gegebn aza LUGGAGE,

00:17:54.122 --> 00:17:58.183
ikh hob ales ongeport, hemder, zoyber, hot zi mir gegebn, ales hob ikh gehat.

00:17:59.370 --> 00:18:04.325
hobn zey gemakht a KRAVA, zey hobn zikh ongehoybn tsu shlogn tsvishn zikh di di soldatn,

00:18:05.108 --> 00:18:09.590
undz ze'mir antlofn, zey hobn genumen, undz hobn aropgevorfn di ale zakhn fun di

00:18:09.664 --> 00:18:12.408
vos zenen geforn, zenen geven merere mentshn,

00:18:12.955 --> 00:18:17.843
un zenen oykh arop geshprungen, zey hobn tsugenumen, az azoy vi vos ikh bin ongekumen oyf Budapest,

00:18:18.000 --> 00:18:21.335
hob ikh nor gehat in di hent deys vos zi hot mir mitgegebn esn.

00:18:21.882 --> 00:18:24.002
m'hot undz gevart dortn mit aza groysn

00:18:24.160 --> 00:18:26.786
shtral-vogn, mit a a ferd,

00:18:26.910 --> 00:18:28.574
m'zol aroyfleygn di zakhn.

00:18:29.796 --> 00:18:31.579
ikh hob nisht gehat vos tsu leygn,

00:18:31.737 --> 00:18:34.785
ikh hob mikh aleyn aroyfgezetst nor mit dem in der hant.

00:18:37.137 --> 00:18:39.729
un azoy ze'mir gevezn in

00:18:39.752 --> 00:18:42.193
Budapest, un m'iz geven in a shul,

00:18:42.216 --> 00:18:45.416
dort iz shoyn gevezn ale vos zikh tsunoyfgekumen,

00:18:45.777 --> 00:18:47.846
dort ho'mir shoyn gevust fun yedn eynem.

00:18:47.852 --> 00:18:52.250
ver s'iz in der heym, un ver s'do, vayl s'geven heymishe mentshn, heymishe dem.

00:18:52.290 --> 00:18:53.780
gevust ver s'shoyn in

00:18:53.780 --> 00:18:57.026
Khust, ver s'shoyn in Koletshave, ales hot men gevust.

00:18:58.129 --> 00:19:00.722
mentshn arumgeforn un zenen gekumen tsurik,

00:19:00.795 --> 00:19:02.847
s'geven mentshn vos hobn shoyn gehandlt,

00:19:03.613 --> 00:19:04.771
in der tsayt,

00:19:05.352 --> 00:19:08.198
s'gevezn ergets in JULY monat,

00:19:12.017 --> 00:19:13.293
un azoy

00:19:14.110 --> 00:19:20.229
ho'mir zikh oyfgezetst oyf a tsug, ikh hob nisht gekent a tsug, di tseger zenen geven iber gelodnt zeyer,

00:19:22.277 --> 00:19:24.161
ikh hob mikh oyfgezetst oyf a tsug fun oyvn,

00:19:24.184 --> 00:19:27.539
oyfn oyf a tsug fun oyvn. keyn zakh hob ikh nisht gehat,

00:19:27.539 --> 00:19:28.970
aroyfgezetst un geforn.

00:19:28.808 --> 00:19:30.658
ver iz geforn mit aykh?

00:19:31.812 --> 00:19:33.375
s'geforn a sakh mentshn.

00:19:32.605 --> 00:19:34.472
ir hot emetsn gekent?

00:19:35.018 --> 00:19:38.336
dort hob ikh gekent mentshn, in dem vos zenen gevezn

00:19:38.460 --> 00:19:40.901
tsuzamen in der shul, ober

00:19:41.413 --> 00:19:46.943
ikh veys nisht der, ikh gedenk shoyn nisht velkhe di mentshn iz geve- ikh bin gekumen oyf Khust,

00:19:48.265 --> 00:19:49.840
vos ikh bin ongekumen deys,

00:19:49.840 --> 00:19:55.886
iz gevezn pinktlekh eyner hot khasene gehat fun undz a koletshaver, er hot, undz ho'mir geven dos dort iz der lebn nokh gegangen,

00:19:56.314 --> 00:19:57.573
bin ikh gekumen hot men mikh

00:19:57.647 --> 00:19:59.551
opgevashn, opgedeyst,

00:19:59.551 --> 00:20:02.416
un ikh bin avekgegangen oyf der khasene, iz gevezn a

00:20:02.760 --> 00:20:07.833
zey zenen hitster in Kanade, Volf.

00:20:10.506 --> 00:20:11.732
un

00:20:13.729 --> 00:20:17.756
fun dort, in Khust iz gevezn a kokh,

00:20:18.606 --> 00:20:21.387
m'iz gekumen in der kokh un m'hot gegesn,

00:20:21.387 --> 00:20:22.953
m'hot gegebn tsu esn,

00:20:23.972 --> 00:20:25.378
mikh tsit aheym!

00:20:25.378 --> 00:20:26.970
ikh UNK ikh gey aheym.

00:20:28.832 --> 00:20:31.132
bin ikh gegangen aheym tsu fus,

00:20:31.132 --> 00:20:32.474
nokh aza deys.

00:20:32.474 --> 00:20:34.901
gegangen biz Derhi far tog,

00:20:35.278 --> 00:20:40.351
dem andern tog bin ikh gegangen oyf dem, s'nisht geven keyn oyto, s'nisht geforn gornisht,

00:20:41.505 --> 00:20:43.642
shoyn far Koletshave

00:20:43.952 --> 00:20:47.810
iz gekumen a a vogn eyner hot mikh oyfgenumen un gebrengt aheym.

00:20:49.217 --> 00:20:52.113
SO bin ikh gekumen aheym, bin ikh arayn in mayn hoyz,

00:20:53.267 --> 00:21:03.875
zi hot mikh zeyer ongenumen, di, zi iz gevezn a slovakishe. Alfons.

00:21:06.868 --> 00:21:08.701
zogt er, koydem

00:21:09.720 --> 00:21:12.245
vos dervayl hostu dayn bet,

00:21:12.538 --> 00:21:14.219
gemakht a zoyber bet,

00:21:15.407 --> 00:21:17.358
un du host dayn bet-gevant,

00:21:17.483 --> 00:21:19.032
host vu tsu shlofn,

00:21:19.032 --> 00:21:20.413
zayn bayn undz.

00:21:21.465 --> 00:21:23.028
azoy bin ikh a por tog,

00:21:23.878 --> 00:21:25.250
ikh hob nisht gedarft gornisht.

00:21:25.212 --> 00:21:27.197
ven ven iz dos geven?

00:21:25.250 --> 00:21:26.302
ikh hob mikh gefreyt,

00:21:27.304 --> 00:21:28.479
velkhn yor?

00:21:27.388 --> 00:21:29.964
dos iz shoyn gevezn finef un fertsiker yor.

00:21:29.751 --> 00:21:32.107
un un velkhn khoydesh?

00:21:31.152 --> 00:21:35.095
naynts- un ere- dos iz gevezn in oygust.

00:21:35.421 --> 00:21:36.832
ven ikh bin aheymgekumen.

00:21:37.260 --> 00:21:40.595
hot ir gehat nayes vegn ayer bruder?

00:21:41.428 --> 00:21:42.215
NO.

00:21:42.525 --> 00:21:45.877
hot ir gevust vos iz geshen mit di gantse mishpokhe?

00:21:46.913 --> 00:21:52.745
po- demolts ho'mir shoyn gevust, vayl s'geven mentshn vos hobn gezogt, vayl zey geven in -zamen mit mayne shvesters.

00:21:53.207 --> 00:21:55.344
zi iz gevezn oykh in an arbets-lager,

00:21:56.211 --> 00:21:58.027
nor eyne iz krank gevorn,

00:21:59.130 --> 00:22:07.713
un m'hot zi gevolt aveknemen, un zey hobn nisht gevolt, zey hobn gezogt zey geyn oykh mit ir, m'hot zey azoy nebekh geharget ales. s'do do in dem iz do mene- froyen velkhe zenen geven tsuzamen.

00:22:07.905 --> 00:22:11.324
azoy hot men ale dray avekgefirt un m'hot zey geharget.

00:22:11.854 --> 00:22:13.957
zikh nisht gevolt iberlozn eyne di andere.

00:22:14.368 --> 00:22:19.728
ven hot ir zikh gekent, ven hot ir oysgefunen vos iz gevorn mit ayer bruder?

00:22:20.325 --> 00:22:24.031
un der bruder iz bin ikh oysgeforn hersht

00:22:25.405 --> 00:22:29.667
in zeks un zibn un fer- zeks un fertsiker yor.

00:22:31.125 --> 00:22:32.446
kh'hob geshribn in

00:22:32.446 --> 00:22:33.785
Roytn Kreyts,

00:22:34.703 --> 00:22:38.443
hob ikh geshribn az s'demolts un demolts iz mayn bruder

00:22:39.124 --> 00:22:44.298
avekgegangen avekgelofn oyf dem, oyf Ru- Rusland,

00:22:44.575 --> 00:22:46.746
un ikh veys nisht gornisht derfun.

00:22:47.612 --> 00:22:50.460
un zey hobn es ibergeshikt oyf

00:22:50.460 --> 00:22:53.090
un m'hot mir geshikt fun fun,

00:22:53.552 --> 00:22:55.267
in Sibir iz er gevezn,

00:22:55.543 --> 00:22:57.444
geshikt funem COURT a

00:22:57.872 --> 00:23:01.173
a deys az er iz geurteylt gevorn

00:23:01.230 --> 00:23:02.591
oyf dray yor,

00:23:03.627 --> 00:23:05.156
un opgezesn iz er zibn.

00:23:06.630 --> 00:23:08.885
gedarft arbeter, m'hot gedeyst.

00:23:09.432 --> 00:23:13.796
SO ven m'hot mir shoyn geshikt dem adres, hob ikh im geshribn,

00:23:14.815 --> 00:23:19.039
er hot mir tsurikgeshribn, un in zibn un fertsik YENER dem fuftstn,

00:23:19.039 --> 00:23:20.681
iz er aheymgekumen.

00:23:22.493 --> 00:23:28.325
ikh hob geshribn in COURT arayn az vi azoy dos iz gevezn vos, SO m'hot im a- aheymgelozt.

00:23:28.703 --> 00:23:31.819
er hot nokh ibergelozt unter zikh mentshn vos velkhe zenen gevezn

00:23:32.787 --> 00:23:36.943
m'hot zey ges- geurteylt far dem vayl zey zenen ariber di grenets nisht LEGAL.

00:23:36.943 --> 00:23:38.012
zenen antlofn.

00:23:40.583 --> 00:23:48.491
un vos ir dertseylt undz di a- ayere iberlebnbungen, vos hot aykh geholfn ongeyn mit ayer lebn?

00:23:54.859 --> 00:23:57.435
s'gevezn in lager

00:23:58.639 --> 00:24:00.894
geven di undzer rebn's a zun,

00:24:03.027 --> 00:24:04.135
Teytlboym,

00:24:05.440 --> 00:24:06.879
er hot undz a sakh...

00:24:06.879 --> 00:24:09.669
un der lager firer iz gevezn a yid eyner,

00:24:11.397 --> 00:24:13.838
a a AUSTRIsher yid.

00:24:15.413 --> 00:24:23.152
er iz geven zeyer a fayner mentsh. er hot gebetn, er hot gehaltn undz droshes, er hot undz gebetn m'zol eyner funem andern nisht tsunemen gornisht.

00:24:23.631 --> 00:24:27.844
do, zogt er, yeder iz in a sekone, yeder iz deys, m'zol zen,

00:24:28.491 --> 00:24:30.192
s'vet zayn a sof,

00:24:30.192 --> 00:24:32.310
un ir vet ale zayn bafrayt,

00:24:32.310 --> 00:24:36.619
un s'geven a a erve yom hakodesh droshe,

00:24:37.840 --> 00:24:39.943
vi er hot undz gegebn farfastn,

00:24:40.152 --> 00:24:42.475
er hot ongeport oyf-fastn,

00:24:42.919 --> 00:24:44.398
m'zol ni- a gantsn tog,

00:24:44.640 --> 00:24:46.051
a'dort geven a por

00:24:46.277 --> 00:24:53.088
azelkhe ungarishe yidn velkhe zey hobn nisht gehaltn gornisht, zey hobn protestirt far vos s'nishto keyn mitog, m'brengt aroyf nor vaser,

00:24:53.668 --> 00:24:55.454
ober dos iberike,

00:24:55.454 --> 00:24:58.196
dos merste iz gevezn vos zey hobn vos zey hobn,

00:24:58.196 --> 00:24:59.822
m'iz aropgegangen oyf der arbet

00:25:01.684 --> 00:25:04.766
un m'iz gegangen oyf der arbet un m'hot gezogt,

00:25:06.156 --> 00:25:07.432
er hot gehat

00:25:07.742 --> 00:25:10.554
nisht a gantsn, a epes a shtik funem makhzer,

00:25:10.830 --> 00:25:14.097
un vi azoy er hot gezogt, yeder hot nokhgezogt in der shure,

00:25:15.353 --> 00:25:16.984
un m'iz gegangen

00:25:18.357 --> 00:25:20.089
un er hot undz gebetn nokh,

00:25:21.141 --> 00:25:23.767
zayne verter, keyn mol vel ikh nisht fargesn, er hot gezogt,

00:25:23.959 --> 00:25:25.843
s'kumt peysekh hitster,

00:25:26.473 --> 00:25:29.099
ikh vel nisht esn, zogt er, keyn khomets,

00:25:29.730 --> 00:25:32.255
ober ikh ken aykh nisht zogn az ir zolt nisht esn.

00:25:33.747 --> 00:25:39.343
eyn zakh bet ikh, ir bakumt dem khomets, zolt ir oyfesn zofort, ir vet nisht avekleygn, vayl ir vet dos nisht zen.

00:25:39.535 --> 00:25:40.896
deys iz zogt er deys.

00:25:42.201 --> 00:25:46.144
er hot nebekh take nokh peysekh iz er oysgegangen, iz er nebekh geshtorbn,

00:25:51.212 --> 00:25:54.817
undz ho'mir aheymgekumen,

00:25:55.363 --> 00:25:56.707
ver s'gekumen,

00:25:58.114 --> 00:26:02.917
ober dos rov fun dey arbeter vos zenen gevezn dort, vos zey hobn nebekh gefirt

00:26:03.193 --> 00:26:04.801
baym evakuirn zikh,

00:26:04.801 --> 00:26:07.237
zenen nisht aheymgekumen, vos zey hobn gezogt,

00:26:07.885 --> 00:26:09.923
ikh hob gevolt nor geyn, m'zol

00:26:09.923 --> 00:26:12.249
un aroystretn oys der shure,

00:26:13.302 --> 00:26:15.011
ikh hob gezogt, ikh vil m'zol mikh

00:26:15.011 --> 00:26:17.261
aropshisn, ikh toyg vayter nisht geyn,

00:26:18.988 --> 00:26:21.496
iz geven dort tsvey brider mit a foter,

00:26:21.570 --> 00:26:23.691
Khaim, un Alter.

00:26:24.844 --> 00:26:29.748
Kalmen, zogt er, undz ve'mir kumen aheym, vos ve'mir undz zogn far dayn mame, az undz hobn dir ibergelozt?

00:26:31.020 --> 00:26:36.046
biz vant undz gey'mir, hobn zey mir ongekhapt unter der dem, un zey hobn mikh nisht gelozt geyn aroys ikh zol mikh...

00:26:36.046 --> 00:26:38.878
ikh hob gevolt nor UNK, ikh hob nisht gevolt vayter lebn.

00:26:40.150 --> 00:26:43.586
ober alts iz gevezn mentshn vos hobn mikh untergedeyst,

00:26:44.824 --> 00:26:46.370
dos hot aykh geholfn?

00:26:48.030 --> 00:26:49.225
der nebekh zenen,

00:26:49.225 --> 00:26:50.977
dem Khaimen hob ikh gezen

00:26:51.608 --> 00:26:53.694
mit a shtik broyt in moyl,

00:26:53.835 --> 00:26:55.179
iz er geshtorbn,

00:26:55.253 --> 00:26:59.803
untern dem in zh- dort in in Ebnze.

00:27:00.501 --> 00:27:03.316
der foter iz geshtorbn hot nisht gekent aribergeyn

00:27:03.316 --> 00:27:05.119
dos vaser,

00:27:05.665 --> 00:27:10.232
un Alter iz nebekh oykh ge- ale zey zenen deys, zenen nisht keyner nisht aheymgekumen.

00:27:11.821 --> 00:27:16.216
vi azoy hot ir gevust az s'iz erev peysekh oder oder yomkiper?

00:27:15.216 --> 00:27:16.610
ho'mir ales gevust.

00:27:16.216 --> 00:27:17.286
vi azoy?

00:27:16.870 --> 00:27:24.899
nu, m'hot gehat tsvishn zikh shokhtim mit rabonim, mit vos, yeder hot ge-, ales ho'mir gevust, ven s'iz purim, ho'mir gevust ven s'iz yeder zakh ho'mir gevust.

00:27:24.767 --> 00:27:27.275
m'hot gedavnt? m'hot gedavnt?

00:27:24.899 --> 00:27:26.195
eyner funem andern.

00:27:26.910 --> 00:27:28.288
oy hot men gedavnt!

00:27:28.227 --> 00:27:30.735
mentshn hobn gehat tfiln?

00:27:30.488 --> 00:27:31.311
NO.

00:27:31.311 --> 00:27:33.536
ikh vey- ikh hob nisht gezen, ken zayn.

00:27:32.361 --> 00:27:36.017
ver ho- ver hot ongefir- emetser hot ongefirt mitn davenen?

00:27:36.512 --> 00:27:46.226
vu hot men gedavnt? m'hot gedavnt in der shure, ven m'iz gegangen oyf der arbet m'hot gedavnt, m'hot ongehoybn eyner un der anderer hot nokhgezogt, s'hot dokh nisht gehat keyn, nisht geven az vos.

00:27:46.401 --> 00:27:50.614
yeder hot gedavnt, un m'hot gezogt vos, vifl m'hot gekent, vos m'hot gekent.

00:27:56.425 --> 00:28:01.940
vos hot ir getun nokh dem vos ir zayt on- ven ir zayt ongekumen in Koletshave?

00:28:01.940 --> 00:28:04.918
un ir hot zikh opgerut bay dem

00:28:04.918 --> 00:28:06.240
in ayer hoyz?

00:28:05.638 --> 00:28:10.107
s'gevezn a lange tsayt vos ikh hob nisht getoygt oyfheybn fun dos bet.

00:28:10.107 --> 00:28:11.539
ikh bin gelegn,

00:28:12.675 --> 00:28:14.863
der hot mir gegebn esn,

00:28:16.354 --> 00:28:20.078
un biz vant ikh bin a bisl tsu mir gekumen,

00:28:22.412 --> 00:28:25.815
ikh bin avekgegangen tsu dem Mihal Shoyen,

00:28:27.947 --> 00:28:31.349
ikh bin shoyn gevoyer gevorn az er iz gegangen, vi bald undz ze'mir

00:28:32.183 --> 00:28:33.814
aribergegangen nor

00:28:33.887 --> 00:28:38.336
di grenets hot er shoyn oyf zikh ibergeshribn dos gantse hoyz, er hot ales

00:28:38.815 --> 00:28:40.597
ibergeshribn oyf zikh,

00:28:41.363 --> 00:28:43.283
zog, vi azoy hostu dos gekent tun?

00:28:43.283 --> 00:28:44.563
du veyst dokh

00:28:45.295 --> 00:28:49.434
az du host fun undz gornisht gegebn, du host far undz nisht gornisht genumen,

00:28:49.434 --> 00:28:52.021
undz hobn dir, ikh hob dir gebrengt dem kontrakt,

00:28:52.855 --> 00:28:53.895
SO vi azoy...

00:28:54.812 --> 00:28:57.472
zogt er, her mikh oys, Kalmen, tsvishn fir oygn,

00:28:58.812 --> 00:29:01.070
ikh veys un ikh,

00:29:01.070 --> 00:29:05.330
ober du v- ikh veys az du vest avekforn avekforn oyf ISRAEL,

00:29:05.330 --> 00:29:06.703
tsi oyf Amerike,

00:29:06.743 --> 00:29:11.917
du vest es dokh mimeyle iberlozn, far vos zol es nisht blaybn far mir, az der mame hot gevolt az s'zol zayn far mir?

00:29:12.261 --> 00:29:14.432
zog ikh, her dikh oys, Sholye Mihal,

00:29:15.028 --> 00:29:18.822
ikh ken dos nisht tun, vayl mayn bruder iz avekgelofn oyf Rusland,

00:29:18.822 --> 00:29:20.357
er vet kumen aheym,

00:29:20.357 --> 00:29:23.611
un er vet nisht visn, er veyst fun dem gantsn gornisht, un er vet

00:29:23.635 --> 00:29:25.333
er vet nisht hobn vu tsu zayn.

00:29:26.841 --> 00:29:29.318
SO du muzt

00:29:29.318 --> 00:29:30.584
dos mir tsurikgebn.

00:29:31.414 --> 00:29:33.655
mir darfn vider baytn dem TA-
